@startuml "Sequence: Query energy consumption"
autonumber
actor "Site Supervisor" as Supervisor
boundary "Frontend Web" as Frontend
control "Telemetry API" as Telemetry
database "Database" as DB
Supervisor -> Frontend : select machine and period
Frontend -> Telemetry : GET /telemetry/machine/{id}/energy
Telemetry -> DB : validate machine and active associated sensor
Telemetry -> DB : query sensor readings by timestamp
Telemetry -> Telemetry : calculate total, average, min, max, count
Telemetry --> Frontend : EnergyConsumption
Frontend --> Supervisor : metrics or empty state
@enduml
